## Rules

- NEVER hardcode versions on `org.springframework.boot` or `org.springframework.cloud` artifacts
- NEVER remove existing exclusions (they are intentional security exclusions)
- NEVER upgrade across Spring Framework major versions unless parent BOM supports it
- ALWAYS keep the `jdk8` classifier on hsqldb
- ALWAYS verify with `mvn clean compile -DskipTests` after changes

## Dry Run Mode

When asked for a "dry run", output the changes as a diff/patch WITHOUT modifying files.
Format: show the BEFORE and AFTER for each `<properties>` section change.
